name: Dinari UFO
description: The Dinari UFO dShares token (UFO.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in the Procure Space ETF (NASDAQ: UFO). This ETF is designed to provide exposure to companies involved in space-related industries, including satellite-based telecommunications, rocket and satellite manufacturing, and space technology and hardware. Each UFO.d token is fully backed by a corresponding UFO ETF share, securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, UFO.d offers investors access to a diversified portfolio of space-related companies, while benefiting from 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
